This should work:

void getmolecularweights_(doublereal* molwts) {
      int nsp = _gas-&gt;nSpecies();
     _gas-&gt;getMolecularWeights(nsp, molwts);
}

The need to pass the number of species to method getMolecularWeights is  
inconsistent with other Cantera methods, and will be changed in a  
future version. But for version 1.5 this will work.

For your SpeciesIndex subroutine, it should be  
_gas-&gt;speciesIndex(string(X, lenx))

Dave


